Case #0172906


Statement of Julia Montauk, regarding her initial encounters with the hunter Trevor Herbert. Statement taken direct from subject, June 29th 2017.



Content Warnings for this episode are at the end of the show notes.


Thanks to this week's Patrons: Linda Evans, Sara Siegmann, Michelle McMullin, Tim, Terence Praet, Alannah Small, Sharon Peterson, Jane Cochard, Bailey Winslow


If you'd like to support us, head to www.patreon.com/rustyquill


Edited this week by Elizabeth Moffatt, Brock Winstead & Alexander J Newall.



Performances:


  •  "The Archivist" - Jonathan Sims
  •  "Julia Montauk" - Francesca Renèe Reid
  •  "Trevor Herbert" - Ian Hayles
  •  "Max Mustermann" - Brock Winstead



Sound effects this week by UOregonCinemaStudies, Straget, lasdimot, MWLAND, and previously credited artists via freesound.org.
